- 1.3g tea leaves / 100g water for black tea. Add 0.2g / 100g for milky
- brew at 84°C for black, 90°C for milky
- [optional] 0.25g coarse chai / 100g water
- 4.5min

Pour initial boiling water over tea leaves to bloom, then pour
remaining water in teapot, then steep wet leaves

With milk
3.5g tea : 200g water, brew 4:30 at 90C 
